title: Course Requirement check for Undergraduate Students
content: To check your course requirement for graduation, send an email to CS department office and visit to see the result. ※ To apply for check up: Send email to csdept@cs.kaist.ac.kr [title]: 2011. 2 Graduation -(student id#)(name)" [content]: name: student id#: registered class for 2010 Fall: cell phone number: date to visit department office (from 2010.9.1 to 2010.9.13 only, at least 1 day after apply) ※Applying period: 2010. 8. 24(tue) ~ 2010. 9. 10(fri) ※For Inquiries: Ms. Haein Chung(042-350-3505)
